PUSHBUTTON "Clear all marks", IDC_CLEAR_MARKS_BUTTON, 207, 99, 60, 14
PUSHBUTTON "Copy Marked Text", IDC_COPY_MARKED_TEXT_BUTTON, 207, 122, 60, 14
